Package: maccaindex
Title: Visualization of Big Index Data And Miscellaneous Functions
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Minh Khanh",
           family = "Pham",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mpham0054@student.monash.edu",
           comment = c(StudentID = "33602875"))
Description: This package contains the 1) Raw data of Big Mac Index from 2011 to 2020; 2) A Shiny App which visualizes this dataset to ignite visual learning, 3) Customizable plotting function which takes in various inputs and display accordingly; and 4) A function can take in either one or two arguments and return a dataframe dependent on the types of the inputs (and how many imputs were called).
